reviews_data.review_text:
Sharetea Review: A Delightful Bubble Tea Experience

Sharetea is a solid choice for bubble tea lovers looking for high-quality drinks with bold flavors and chewy tapioca pearls. Their menu offers a great variety, from classic milk teas to fruit-infused options and even some creative blends.

Flavor & Quality: The drinks are well-balanced in sweetness and tea flavor, and the boba pearls are consistently fresh and chewy. One standout is the Classic Pearl Milk Tea, which has a smooth, rich taste that isn’t overly sweet. The Wintermelon Tea with Creama is another favorite, offering a perfect mix of sweet and creamy.

Customization: I appreciate the ability to adjust sweetness and ice levels, which makes it easier to tailor drinks to your taste. They also offer different toppings, like pudding, herbal jelly, and aloe vera, for extra texture.

Service & Ambiance: The staff is friendly and efficient, and the drinks are prepared quickly. The shop itself (depending on location) is usually clean and modern, with a casual and welcoming vibe.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Thank you Ravyn for taking the time to wrote this amazing and thoughtful review! We are thrilled that you and all of our customers love the variety and customization of drinks! Not to mention our amazing staff! Thank you again for sharing your experiences with us and the rest of Charlotte community!

We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text:
Sharetea Review: A Delightful Bubble Tea Experience

Sharetea is a solid choice for bubble tea lovers looking for high-quality drinks with bold flavors and chewy tapioca pearls. Their menu offers a great variety, from classic milk teas to fruit-infused options and even some creative blends.

Flavor & Quality: The drinks are well-balanced in sweetness and tea flavor, and the boba pearls are consistently fresh and chewy. One standout is the Classic Pearl Milk Tea, which has a smooth, rich taste that isn’t overly sweet. The Wintermelon Tea with Creama is another favorite, offering a perfect mix of sweet and creamy.

Customization: I appreciate the ability to adjust sweetness and ice levels, which makes it easier to tailor drinks to your taste. They also offer different toppings, like pudding, herbal jelly, and aloe vera, for extra texture.

Service & Ambiance: The staff is friendly and efficient, and the drinks are prepared quickly. The shop itself (depending on location) is usually clean and modern, with a casual and welcoming vibe.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Thank you Ravyn for taking the time to wrote this amazing and thoughtful review! We are thrilled that you and all of our customers love the variety and customization of drinks! Not to mention our amazing staff! Thank you again for sharing your experiences with us and the rest of Charlotte community!

We hope to see you again soon!

I stopped by for the first time on Tuesday, 05-28-24. I had water, but it was hot & I wanted something else cold and refreshing. I was torn between the mango and passion fruit green tea and the tea with kiwi and some type of jelly. The young lady taking my order suggested the mango and passion fruit because she didn't like the kiwi seeds. This one had what I believed to be passion fruit seeds in it, but seeds don't bother me at all.

I went with her suggestion of mango & passion fruit green tea. I did 50% sweetness. The tea was soo good & with plenty of sweetness. At a price of $6.25, this would just be an occasional splurge. I'd definitely return to try other flavors and drinks.
